version_description:
Our little elves have been working days and nights on this one! We're proud to present the brand new addition to your app: Charge My Car.
Electric charging has just became much easier with this new service. Find one of 195'000 electric charging stations available. Book and pay directly from your App. How cool is that ?

Aside from this great news, we also added some new features :
You can now easily check the level of charge or fuel of the carsharing vehicles directly by looking at its pin
We enhanced the license scanning flow to make it as fast as it gets when registering on the App.
And of course, we adjusted some lines of codes here and there to make your App even better.
